<%- include('partials/header') %>
<section class="page-hero page-hero-home">
  <p class="eyebrow">Garden OS</p>
  <h1>Run Your Garden Like A Calm, Clear Workflow</h1>
  <p class="hero-copy">Map beds, manage each plant profile, and keep daily care visible without getting lost in cluttered screens or giant tables.</p>
  <div class="hero-grid">
    <article class="hero-stat-card">
      <p>Tracked plants</p>
      <strong><%= plantCount %></strong>
    </article>
    <article class="hero-stat-card">
      <p>Active reminders</p>
      <strong><%= reminderCount %></strong>
    </article>
    <article class="hero-stat-card">
      <p>Next best step</p>
      <strong><%= plantCount > 0 ? 'Check reminders' : 'Add first plant' %></strong>
    </article>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-actions">
    <a class="btn" href="/garden-plan">Open Garden Planner</a>
    <a class="btn" href="/plants/add">Add a Plant</a>
    <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/plants">Open Collection</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cards tri-grid">
  <article class="card workflow-card">
    <p class="eyebrow">01</p>
    <h2>Design The Space</h2>
    <p>Draw your garden shape and place markers for growing zones, irrigation, and compost.</p>
    <a href="/garden-plan">Open Planner</a>
  </article>

  <article class="card workflow-card">
    <p class="eyebrow">02</p>
    <h2>Track Each Plant</h2>
    <p>Keep species identity, care conditions, toxicity, and notes in one clear collection view.</p>
    <a href="/plants">Open Plants</a>
  </article>

  <article class="card workflow-card">
    <p class="eyebrow">03</p>
    <h2>Work The Schedule</h2>
    <p>Use reminders as your operational view for watering, feeding, weeding, and pruning.</p>
    <a href="/reminders">Open Reminders</a>
  </article>
</section>

<section class="cards dual-grid">
  <article class="card">
    <h2>Plant Database</h2>
    <p>Need better taxonomy data before adding a new profile? Use the database to browse and prefill entries quickly.</p>
    <a href="/plant-database">Browse Plant Database</a>
  </article>
  <article class="card">
    <h2>Collection First UX</h2>
    <p>The collection page is redesigned for scanning, not spreadsheet reading, so decisions take less time.</p>
    <a href="/plants">See Collection Design</a>
  </article>
</section>
<%- include('partials/footer') %>
